{"tid":1291632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.7] 有閞7.7遊行 有藍色/黑幫打人問題","createTime":"2019-07-07T03:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T05:34:00.000Z","uid":94771,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8cdc84c3df9de4ae7fb71b31c927d59e13c3f6dc","tid":1291632,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:32:48.000Z","msg":"如果你影到人打你<br />\n你還手都可以叫自衛 報出來都有理由比文宣還手<br />\n影唔到人打你 走去圍打人 新聞睇落去就變暴徒 <br />\n到時全民意lost 就準備每次得幾百人遊行 依邊變過街老鼠<br />\n之後你地就只可以笑人普遍大眾港猪 準備移民<br />\n<br />\n請以大局為重<br />\n我發現連登勇武愈來愈激 好似咩都唔想理咁 重知就激左先 <br />\n出佐氣就OK <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係話唔還得手 但發夢還手之前請準備對家打人証據 令自己有還手合理性<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要勇武都聰明D 唔好頭腦發熱 死衝爛衝</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"88be10ba65e2e658e76a5843e1daf972c1a506b1","tid":1291632,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85388a32bec9a4ae03fd4223b7029de9575d442","tid":1291632,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5d70b30172bed49dc8bd34c4905e19693b8f55","tid":1291632,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5b4f08c9cfb3b2facd35521dfc13f29b4a9628","tid":1291632,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201decbce76d03e093140676074dad4128ffd18f","tid":1291632,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f87bf79ccd0ca87c96ba3c1caa2192e10d0b03","tid":1291632,"uid":94771,"like":0,"d