:1291632,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"衝立會都係暴徒，612都係暴，樓主快啲同呢場運動割蓆，保持優雅。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"割你老母<br />\n我認同7.1衝立會<br />\n但我唔認同無理由咁影響大局<br />\n<br />\n同埋我都話佐 勇武唔係唔得 <br />\n但請聰明D 唔好頭腦發熱 死衝爛衝<br />\n<br />\n定你覺得你死衝爛衝先好"},{"pid":"f3eb28fcffd783b559f234c6f8a2bebcfb45ae65","tid":1291632,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:34:00.000Z","msg":"1240更新 -<br />\n由於高鐵站已被水馬重重圍封，遊行人士於終點的集合場地範圍將會大大地被縮小。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>高鐵站唯一入口 -</strong></span><br />\n佐敦道/柯士甸站B5 &gt; 佐敦道行人天橋 ＞ 入㘣方直行 ＞ 落地下大快活出口 ＞ 高鐵站D入口<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">高鐵站唯一出口 -</span></strong><br />\n高鐵站L1 &gt; 往佐敦道行人天橋(可出巴士總站/柯士甸B5出口/佐敦道)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VopXRm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VopXRm.png&h=33f7ab72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKF7VC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKF7VC3.jpg&h=81dcaa48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gcDUAC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcDUAC5.jpg&h=6e51d40d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtH6rKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtH6rKM.jpg&h=b2c0afeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zmTQTpO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzmTQTpO.jpg&h=12953117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5WrrKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5WrrKP.jpg&h=9c7d86dc&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"}]}